      <title>沙特阿拉伯同意与 Topgolf Callaway 合作建造高尔夫球场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/saudi-arabia-agrees-to-build-golf-venues-with-topgolf-callaway</link>
